      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the use of the Stac LZS data compression algorithm for compressing PPP encapsulated packets, using a DCP header [6].  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
